@Jack Fox 
You mentioned the race between China and the US.  How much of the world's clean metals does the US produce?  You make an excellent point about the China's air quality.  Do you think China is processing these metals in order to positively impact the environment?  DRC produces so much cobalt because that is where it is naturally found.  Why do you think they then send it to China to process?
I like your catchy headline!
